summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Thirty-second Avenue Northwest from West 57th Street to West 64th Street et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 17473, creating Local Improvement District No. 1654 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
